nodes.text: Assure Our Victory! was a propaganda poster created by Simeon Densend during the Clone Wars. At the top, it says "Narglatch AirTech reminds you to:", and then in big font requests that the reader "Slow Your Speed and Share Your Speeder" with it showing a speeding XJ-6 airspeeder with two passengers inside, and below it in big yellow font it stated "Assure Our Victory!", with the "V" being stylized to include a yellow streak. The very bottom had the words "Commute", "Conserve", and "Contribute."
